HEADWORD: Choke-strap
<hw>Choke"-strap`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Saddlery)</fld>
<def>A strap leading from the bellyband to the lower part of the collar,
to keep the collar in place.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

